dc_description_s: India. Bombay City and Suburbs Post-War Development Committee. Companion text: Greater Bombay scheme. Preliminary report of the Communications (Traffic and Railways) Panel. [Bombay]: Bombay City and Suburbs Post-War Development Committee. 1945. 37p. illus., folded map. In lower right margin: "Govt: Photo-Zinco Press, Poona. 1946." Shows existing and proposed ferry routes. Map Library does not have the accompanying report.
